eventData.messageText:
And thus begins our hero's quest.

Young Kieran had everything in life. Obnoxiously loud
speakers, a loving family (*cough*) and a demigod bod.





Were it not for the fact that his internet moved at a
snail's pace, then Kieran would be content and normal.





But the forces above have CURSED Kieran with a terrible,
terrible fate.





When creating Kieran in his image, God realized that
the child would be too powerful, too 'hip'.





So then, he bestowed a mighty CURSE upon Kieran.





"The Flood 2.0 will transpire,
should Kieran conquer optic wire.
The man makes the ladies wet,
for that he shan't have internet."




And with that...



With this basic necessity of life, stripped from him
at birth...



Kieran sought to reclaim what was rightfully his.








 --------- TWO WEEKS EARLIER -----------

(actually the end of the current patch lmao)
